    <title>CentOS 7 Minimal架站技術篇/2019-11-02_CentOS 7 Minimal架站技術篇(一)  安裝CentOS 7 Minimal 作業系統</title>
    <link href="http://cooljohnny.github.io/2019/11/02/CentOS%207%20Minimal%E6%9E%B6%E7%AB%99%E6%8A%80%E8%A1%93%E7%AF%87/2019-11-02_CentOS%207%20Minimal%E6%9E%B6%E7%AB%99%E6%8A%80%E8%A1%93%E7%AF%87(%E4%B8%80)%20%20%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%9DCentOS%207%20Minimal%20%E4%BD%9C%E6%A5%AD%E7%B3%BB%E7%B5%B1/"/>
    <id>http://cooljohnny.github.io/2019/11/02/CentOS 7 Minimal架站技術篇/2019-11-02_CentOS 7 Minimal架站技術篇(一)  安裝CentOS 7 Minimal 作業系統/</id>
    <published>2019-11-01T16:00:00.000Z</published>
    <updated>2019-11-10T14:47:57.733Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="環境架設"><a href="#環境架設" class="headerlink" title="環境架設"></a>環境架設</h1><p>1、Windows 10 企業版 1803<br>2、虛擬主機 VirtualBox-6.0.14-133895<br><a href="https://download.virtualbox.org/virtualbox/6.0.14/VirtualBox-6.0.14-133895-Win.exe" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://download.virtualbox.org/virtualbox/6.0.14/VirtualBox-6.0.14-133895-Win.exe</a><br>3、CentOS-7-x86_64-Minimal-1908.iso<br><a href="http://mirror.team-cymru.com/CentOS/7.7.1908/isos/x86_64/CentOS-7-x86_64-Minimal-1908.iso" target="_blank" rel="noopener">http://mirror.team-cymru.com/CentOS/7.7.1908/isos/x86_64/CentOS-7-x86_64-Minimal-1908.iso</a></p><h1 id="開啟VirtualBox"><a href="#開啟VirtualBox" class="headerlink" title="開啟VirtualBox"></a>開啟VirtualBox</h1><p>1、新增一台虛擬主機<br><img src="/images/YUNYU-JOHNNY-PC-2.jpg" alt="YUNYU-JOHNNY-P"></p><p>2、設置記憶體<br><img src="/images/YUNYU-JOHNNY-PC-3.jpg" alt="YUNYU-JOHNNY-P"></p><p>3、設置硬碟容量<br><img src="/images/YUNYU-JOHNNY-PC-4.jpg" alt="YUNYU-JOHNNY-P"></p><p>4、選擇硬碟檔類型<br><img src="/images/YUNYU-JOHNNY-PC-5.jpg" alt="YUNYU-JOHNNY-P"></p><p>5、選擇存放裝置實體硬碟中<br><img src="/images/YUNYU-JOHNNY-PC-6.jpg" alt="YUNYU-JOHNNY-P"></p><p>6、建立虛擬硬體大小，改為40GB<br><img src="/images/YUNYU-JOHNNY-PC-7.jpg" alt="YUNYU-JOHNNY-P"></p><p>7、載入光碟檔案：CentOS-7-x86_64-Minimal-1908.iso<br><img src="/images/YUNYU-JOHNNY-PC-8.jpg" alt="YUNYU-JOHNNY-P"></p><h1 id="開始安裝CentOS-7"><a href="#開始安裝CentOS-7" class="headerlink" title="開始安裝CentOS 7"></a>開始安裝CentOS 7</h1><p>1、選擇「Install CentOs 7」<br><img src="/images/YUNYU-JOHNNY-PC-9.jpg" alt="YUNYU-JOHNNY-P"></p><p>2、出現選擇安裝語言，選擇(English」後，按下「Continue」<br><img src="/images/YUNYU-JOHNNY-PC-11.jpg" alt="YUNYU-JOHNNY-P"></p><p>3、初始化設定，先選擇「DATE &amp; TIME」<br><img src="/images/YUNYU-JOHNNY-PC-12.jpg" alt="YUNYU-JOHNNY-P"></p><p>4、Region選擇「Asia」, City選擇「Taipei」，然後按「Done」<br><img src="/images/YUNYU-JOHNNY-PC-13.jpg" alt="YUNYU-JOHNNY-P"></p><p>5、確認時區設定已被改為「Asia/Taipei Timezone」<br><img src="/images/YUNYU-JOHNNY-PC-14.jpg" alt="YUNYU-JOHNNY-P"></p><p>6、接下來設定安裝磁碟，選擇INSTALLATION DESTINATION]<br><img src="/images/YUNYU-JOHNNY-PC-15.jpg" alt="YUNYU-JOHNNY-P"></p><p>7、選擇「Automatically configure partitioning」，再按「Done」<br><img src="/images/YUNYU-JOHNNY-PC-16.jpg" alt="YUNYU-JOHNNY-P"></p><p>8、設定網路位址，方便連接網際網路，選擇「NETWORK &amp; HOST NAME」<br><img src="/images/YUNYU-JOHNNY-PC-17.jpg" alt="YUNYU-JOHNNY-P"></p><p>9、點選「Configure…」<br><img src="/images/YUNYU-JOHNNY-PC-18.jpg" alt="YUNYU-JOHNNY-P"></p><p>10 、點選「IPv4 Settings」<br><img src="/images/YUNYU-JOHNNY-PC-19.jpg" alt="YUNYU-JOHNNY-P"></p><p>11、Method選擇「Manual」手動設定，按「Add」按鈕設定IP位址，並且設定DNS server位址，最後按下「Save」按鈕<br><img src="/images/YUNYU-JOHNNY-PC-20.jpg" alt="YUNYU-JOHNNY-P"></p><p>12、點選開關按鈕，將網路卡設定「ON」，可看見IP已正常運作後，按「Done」<br><img src="/images/YUNYU-JOHNNY-PC-21.jpg" alt="YUNYU-JOHNNY-P"></p><p>13、完成相關設定後，可看到「SOFTWARE SELECTION」預設為「Minimal Install」，接下來按「Begin Installation」按鈕來開始安裝CentOS。<br><img src="/images/YUNYU-JOHNNY-PC-22.jpg" alt="YUNYU-JOHNNY-P"></p><p>14、設定root帳號密通四，點選「ROOT PASSWORD」<br><img src="/images/YUNYU-JOHNNY-PC-23.jpg" alt="YUNYU-JOHNNY-P"></p><p>15、設定「Root Password」和「Confirm」的密碼一定要一樣，而且要記好，如果是要上線的機器，要設定複雜的密碼，以免被駭客猜中密碼入侵，設定好密碼後，再按「Done」<br><img src="/images/YUNYU-JOHNNY-PC-24.jpg" alt="YUNYU-JOHNNY-P"></p><p>16、接下來按下「Finsh configuaration」<br><img src="/images/YUNYU-JOHNNY-PC-25.jpg" alt="YUNYU-JOHNNY-P"></p><p>17、大約等待安裝時間約3分鐘左右可能更快，然後按下「Reboot」<br><img src="/images/YUNYU-JOHNNY-PC-26.jpg" alt="YUNYU-JOHNNY-P"></p><p>18、如出現下圖畫面，恭禧您，已成功安裝CentOS 7 Minimal，可以繼續後面的伺服器軟體安裝或系統設定嚕！<br> <img src="/images/YUNYU-JOHNNY-PC-27.jpg" alt="YUNYU-JOHNNY-P"></p>]]></content>
    
