  <entry>
    <title>CentOS 7 Minimal架站技術篇/2019-11-01_CentOS 7 Minimal架站技術篇(目錄)</title>
    <link href="http://cooljohnny.github.io/2019/11/01/CentOS%207%20Minimal%E6%9E%B6%E7%AB%99%E6%8A%80%E8%A1%93%E7%AF%87/2019-11-01_CentOS%207%20Minimal%E6%9E%B6%E7%AB%99%E6%8A%80%E8%A1%93%E7%AF%87(%E7%9B%AE%E9%8C%84)/"/>
    <id>http://cooljohnny.github.io/2019/11/01/CentOS 7 Minimal架站技術篇/2019-11-01_CentOS 7 Minimal架站技術篇(目錄)/</id>
